    <div class="card-category offset" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1535813449-9b1b28174821?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1534&q=80)">
      Get advises from locals
    </div>

    <div class="card-category" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1470010762743-1fa2363f65ca?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=60)">
